        </li>
        <li><b>Personal use</b> - fee will be added for based on complexity</li>
        <li>
          <b>Commercial use</b> - extra fee will be added, to be discussed privately
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h2>General Info</h2>
      <p>
        I tend to be very friendly, so I'm sorry if I come off as
        unprofessional! (✿◡‿◡)
      </p>
      <ul class="general-info-list">
        <li>☑️ An <b>extra character</b> costs 75% of the original price</li>
        <li>☑️ Can provide WIPs or sketches <small>if requested</small></li>
        <li>☑️ Turnaround from 1 week to 3 months</li>
        <li>
          ☑️ Commissions are <b>non-refundable</b>, unless the turnaround date
          has passed or the client has an emergency
        </li>
        <li>
          ☑️ If you don't want your commission to be posted, streamed or shared,
          please notify me beforehand
        </li>
        <li>
          ❎ Do not request a deadline and put pressure on me to work, I like to
          provide the highest quality on my work
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h2>✔️ DOs</h2>
      <ul class="dos-list">
        <li>OCs</li>
        <li>Fanart</li>
        <li>Game characters</li>
        <li>
          Kemonomimi <span class="reference"
            ><a
              href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moe_anthropomorphism#Animals"
              target="_blank"
              >[Ref]</a
            ></span>
        </li>
        <li>Anthros <span class="reference"
            ><a
              href="https://en.wikifur.com/wiki/Anthropomorphic"
              target="_blank"
              >[Ref]</a
            ></span></li>
      </ul>
      <h2>✖️ DONTs</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Elderly</li>
        <li>NSFW</li>
        <li>Facial hair</li>
        <li>Anything I might feel uncomfortable drawing</li>
        <li>Written out description of OCs (depends)</li>
      </ul>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body><style>
    .text-with-svg svg {
      position: relative;
      top: 5px;
      width: 1.2rem;
      height: 1.2rem;
    }

    .general-info-list li {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .reference a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-decoration: none;
	  color: hsl(260 70% 40%);
	  font-weight: 900;
    }

	.reference a:hover {
		opacity: .75;
	}
  </style>
</html>
